			<div class="clear"></div>
			<div id="category-name">
		<h1 class="title">Sojurn &#8211; The TV App</h1>
		
				<p class="meta-info">
					Posted  by <a href="http://www.jarloo.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by Kelly Elias" rel="author">Kelly Elias</a> on May 14, 2013 in <a href="http://www.jarloo.com/category/code/" title="View all posts in Code Snippets" rel="category tag">Code Snippets</a>, <a href="http://www.jarloo.com/category/featured/" title="View all posts in Featured" rel="category tag">Featured</a>, <a href="http://www.jarloo.com/category/code/projects/" title="View all posts in Projects" rel="category tag">Projects</a>, <a href="http://www.jarloo.com/category/tutorials/" title="View all posts in Tutorials" rel="category tag">Tutorials</a>, <a href="http://www.jarloo.com/category/code/wpf/" title="View all posts in WPF" rel="category tag">WPF</a> | <a href="http://www.jarloo.com/sojurn-the-tv-app/#comments" title="Comment on Sojurn &#8211; The TV App">6 comments</a>			</p>
	</div> <!-- end #category-name -->					
			
