						<div class="comment-content"><p>Your looking for the MemoryStream. Take this code from Sojurn and replace the FileStream with a MemoryStream and it will not write to disk but still load into the ImageSource. Keep in mind each image consumes memory so you can&#8217;t show thousands at once.</p>
<p><code>Stream imageStreamSource = new FileStream(filename, FileMode.Open, FileAccess.Read, FileShare.Read);<br />
PngBitmapDecoder decoder = new PngBitmapDecoder(imageStreamSource, BitmapCreateOptions.PreservePixelFormat, BitmapCacheOption.Default);<br />
e.ImageSource = decoder.Frames[0];</code></p>
